WEBVTT

00:01.879 --> 00:04.056
Previously on Once Upon A Time...

00:04.056 --> 00:04.961
It's Marian.

00:04.961 --> 00:06.730
He's honor-bound to stay with her.

00:06.865 --> 00:08.369
Therefore, I have to save her.

00:08.518 --> 00:09.852
Why the hell are you following me?!

00:09.887 --> 00:12.188
I'm starting to think maybe
it wasn't just some curse

00:12.222 --> 00:13.355
that brought her to Storybrooke.

00:13.390 --> 00:15.992
- Where is she?
- She's gone.

00:17.759 --> 00:22.123
